description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking a&lt;strong&gt;Cardiac Physiologist | Echo Physiologist&lt;/strong&gt;to join the Omnes Healthcare Family; become part of a company that makes a difference.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Part Time hours available for North East London - 10 hours a week (can accommodate Monday - Friday)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;£45,000 per annum depending on experience&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have fully COVID compliant infection control policies in place.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Omnes Healthcare Limited are operating within the NHS to provide personalised, quality healthcare services and have been doing so since 2006. We aim to develop supportive, genuine relationships with every patient, physician, nurse and healthcare professional that we come into contact with. We believe each patient is unique and deserves treatment that is both effective, heartfelt and has a positive outcome on their well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you join us, you&#39;ll be part of something special–an innovative and rapidly growing organisation where we know that the finest patient care comes from empowering our teams to be the very best at what they do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is the purpose of the position?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are seeking a committed BSE accredited Cardiac Physiologist or to join a committed team working within the NHS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the key responsibilities?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To be an effective member of the Cardiology team, providing the highest standard of cardiology service to patients in our expanding cardiology service, working autonomously in a community setting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post-holder will report to the Operations Service Manager and will work closely with internal and external business partners to continually develop the cardiology service, in line with agreed aims and objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post holder will contribute to optimising the patient pathway and the efficiency of the cardiology service, and safeguard best practice in overall performance and finance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post-holder will actively seek ways of reducing outgoings by developing new ways of working and positively contribute to the cardiology team to deliver maximum efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do you need to join the Omnes Healthcare Family?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current GMC Registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidates must have experience in performing Echocardiogram, 12 Lead ECG and be able to interpret all diagnostics including 24 hour ECG, 24 Hour blood pressure monitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Omnes Healthcare will offer you in return?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days holiday plus bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An extra day off to celebrate your birthday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And other benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Apply today if you want to make a difference.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We believe in innovation; we believe in listening to everyone; we believe in providing quality service; and we believe our employees will help us achieve our mission.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please be aware that all communications about this vacancy will be received to you via email. Always check your mail box and junk mail folders and provide a UK mobile number if available.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
